NOTICE:

While this script might still work, it hasn't been maintained for the last 7 years.
For a more recent alternative, try https://github.com/matlink/gplaycli.

---

GooglePlay Downloader - Directly download apks from GooglePlay to your PC.
by Simone Margaritelli aka evilsocket
<evilsocket@gmail.com - http://www.evilsocket.net>

Given you GooglePlay access data and a package name, this script will generate a http
link for you to directly download th APK file to your computer instead of installing
it on your device.

For the help menu please type:

  python gplay-downloader.py --help
